node.text: My friend @josephreiver has been running this garden in SoHo NY for years as a public space for all to enjoy in the city and it’s at risk of being bought up by developers and turned into housing.  It currently has over 100k visitors a year and 200 free programs in gardening, education, wellness and arts.  Please donate if you can.  It’s a beautiful space.  If you’re in NYC go check it out @elizabethstreetgarden
